company_name: LANDWIRTSCHAFTLICHE VIEH- UND FLEISCHVERMARKTUNG WALDECK-WOLFHAGEN EG
information: The company LANDWIRTSCHAFTLICHE VIEH- UND FLEISCHVERMARKTUNG WALDECK-WOLFHAGEN EG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1928, which operates in the Meat industry. It also operates in the Sheep and goats industries. It is based in Bad Arolsen, Germany.
